title: Wow Multi boxing: Autoconnection and foot control of the focus.
description: No the best video I have done but I need it for the archived. It is a demo of how you can auto-log and manage multi-game-account with multiboxing in round robin style with OMI.  Everything is bugging due to OBS +3 Wow window using lot's of the CPU.
